00:01:16.559 --> 00:01:21.760
industries, chat about data science leadership, and connect with other people who are facing

00:01:21.760 --> 00:01:27.680
things similar as you. And we get together here every Thursday at the same time, same place. So

00:01:27.680 --> 00:01:33.120
if you're watching this as a recording on YouTube, and you want to join us live in the future,

00:01:33.120 --> 00:01:38.080
there will be details below to add it to your own calendar. And this is just a double check

00:01:38.080 --> 00:01:45.279
for everybody. Just make sure it's adding it from 12 to 1 Eastern Time. I know sometimes something's

00:01:45.279 --> 00:01:50.239
happening if people were like traveling when they added it, and it's staying in whatever time zone.

00:01:50.239 --> 00:01:56.800
We all know how much fun time zones are to work with. But thank you so much to everybody who has

00:01:56.800 --> 00:02:02.480
helped make this the friendly and welcoming space that it is today. And we are all dedicated to

00:02:02.480 --> 00:02:08.080
