me anonymously, good or bad, or any suggestions, Zoom will actually automatically launch a survey

00:02:15.119 --> 00:02:20.800
right when you end the Hangout as well. You can always reach out to me directly on LinkedIn too.

00:02:22.639 --> 00:02:27.440
Yeah, same. And at the Hangout, we love hearing from you. It doesn't matter your years of experience,

00:02:27.440 --> 00:02:31.919
what your title is, what industry you're in, what language you work in or don't work in.

00:02:32.720 --> 00:02:38.000
And we really encourage you to connect in the chat. This is a space for all of us to hang out

00:02:38.000 --> 00:02:44.960
together. So briefly introduce yourself, add a LinkedIn profile link, maybe add your website,

00:02:44.960 --> 00:02:51.199
just some way to get a hold of you and show who you are. Because this chat moves quickly and then

00:02:51.199 --> 00:02:59.279
it goes away. So we want to make sure we stay connected after today. Let's see, we are also

00:02:59.279 --> 00:03:05.039
going to try to grab questions from the chat. So this is the way that the Hangout works. It is an

00:03:05.039 --> 00:03:12.880
open discussion from the community moderated by Rachel and I. So it doesn't happen unless you ask

