next to it or in parentheses, like I can't use my mic right now, we'll ask it for you.

00:03:31.440 --> 00:03:36.720
And then there's also a Slido link that's going to be in the chat. Isabella just put it in there,

00:03:36.720 --> 00:03:41.279
where you can ask questions anonymously if you like. And we'll try to get to as many questions

00:03:41.279 --> 00:03:44.479
as we can. Sometimes we have way too many, but that's okay, keep them coming.

00:03:45.919 --> 00:03:53.119
Perfect. I'm going to do one quick shout out here that the call for talks for PositComp 2025

